column5: I am looking for a nice lodge with good fishing. I have been twice to Chaudiere loved the place just have had no luck with the fishing. Even guided so it's not just me lol  Any suggestions for the second week of July?  Thanks in advance Linda
Calling DR. MIKE BORGER, DR. BORGER.You are needed in the plan a trip room. Calling DR. BORGER.
DR BORGER, is doing fish surgery, will be out soon, stand by, have your symptoms ready for diagnosis.
